room_title: Escape room "Interrogation" by Crisis Rooms in Frankfort
room_address: 20861 South La Grange Road Frankfort, IL 60423
room_description: The business of the FBI is of the utmost importance and extremely classified. Even still, it does not mean that the Agents are above the law. That is why when allegations of corruption were brought against the office, your team from Internal Affairs was brought in to investigate.  Your team has come into the office unannounced and immediately evacuated the building so no one would not have any time to destroy evidence. You have 60 Minutes to complete your investigation and determine if there is any truth to these allegations, or is it all unfounded?
